+func (e *endpoint) DeleteTemplate(ctx *gin.Context) {
+
+ var inputVM *DeleteTemplateInputVM
+ if err := ctx.Bind(&inputVM); err != nil {
+ errno.Failed(http.StatusBadRequest, errno.ErrBind, err, ctx)
+ return
+ }
+
+ var inputDto = &odds.DeleteTemplateInputDto{
+ TemplateID: inputVM.TemplateID,
+ }
+
+ outputDto, errcode := e.oddsHdr.DeleteTemplate(inputDto)
+
+ if errcode > 0 {
+ logger.Error(fmt.Sprintf("endpoints/odds/DeleteTemplate error: %v", errcode))
+ errno.FailedCode(http.StatusOK, errcode, ctx)
+ } else {
+ var outputVM = &DeleteTemplateOutputVM{
+ TemplateID: outputDto.TemplateID,
+ }
+ errno.Success(outputVM, ctx)
+ }
+
+}
+
+// swagger:operation delete /odds/template odds DeleteTemplate
+//
+// 樣板刪除

+func (e *endpoint) GetTemplateLeagues(ctx *gin.Context) {
+
+ var inputVM *GetTemplateLeaguesInputVM

+ errno.Failed(http.StatusBadRequest, errno.ErrBind, err, ctx)
+ return
+ }
+
+ if inputVM.Per == 0 {

+ }
+
+ var inputDto = &odds.GetTemplateLeaguesInputDto{
+ SportID: inputVM.SportID,
+ TemplateID: inputVM.TemplateID,
+ LeagueIDs: inputVM.LeagueIDs,
+ Pagination: inputVM.Pagination,
+ }
+
+ outputDto, errcode, count := e.oddsHdr.GetTemplateLeagues(inputDto)
+
+ if errcode > 0 {
+ logger.Error(fmt.Sprintf("endpoints/odds/GetTemplateLeagues error: %v", errcode))
+ errno.FailedCode(http.StatusOK, errcode, ctx)
+ } else {
+ var outputVM GetTemplateLeaguesOutputVM
+ outputVM.GetTemplateLeaguesOutputDto = outputDto
+ errno.SuccessPager(outputVM, count, ctx)

+func searchCeiling(ladder []uint, target uint) uint { //傳入的ladder必須由小到大排列且不可重複
+
+ l := 0
+ r := len(ladder) - 1
+
+ mid := (l + r) / 2
+
+ for l <= r {
+
+ if ladder[mid] == target {
+ return ladder[mid]
+ }
+ if ladder[mid] > target {
+ r = mid - 1
+ } else {
+ l = mid + 1
+ }
+ mid = (r + l) / 2
+ }
+
+ if mid != len(ladder)-1 && target > ladder[mid] {
+ mid++
+ }
+
+ return ladder[mid]

+// Sheet 梯度表單物件
+type Sheet struct {
+ LadderID uint
+ LadderName string
+ OptionCount int
+ IsDefault bool
+ Lads []Lad //ordered by prob
+}
+
+// Lad 梯度表
+type Lad struct {
+ Prob float64
+ JtoO JuiceOdds // [3]float64 is like for homeOdds,awayOdds,drawOdds
+}
+
+// LadderSheets 梯度表
+type LadderSheets struct {
+ Sheets []Sheet
+}
+
+//GetLadderSheetObj 梯度表物件
+func GetLadderSheetObj() (sheets LadderSheets, err error) {
+ jsonFile, err := os.Open("data/ladder_sheet.json") //專案實體檔案
+ if err != nil {
+ logger.Error("open ladder json file error")
+ return
+ }
+ byteValue, err := ioutil.ReadAll(jsonFile)
+ if err != nil {
+ logger.Error("read ladder json file error")
+ return
+ }
+ err = json.Unmarshal(byteValue, &sheets)
+ if err != nil {
+ logger.Error("unmarshal ladder json file error")
+ return
+ }
+
+ //golang浮點會有trailing number 需要做四捨五入
+ for idx1 := range sheets.Sheets {
+ for idx2 := range sheets.Sheets[idx1].Lads {
+ //oldProb := sheets.Sheets[idx1].Lads[idx2].Prob
+ newProb := math.Round(sheets.Sheets[idx1].Lads[idx2].Prob*100) / 100
+ //fmt.Println(oldProb)
+ //fmt.Println(newProb)
+ sheets.Sheets[idx1].Lads[idx2].Prob = newProb
+ }
+ }
+
+ //用search ceiling的邏輯來拿掉重複的row
+ for idx := range sheets.Sheets {
+ addrLad := &sheets.Sheets[idx]
+ len := len(addrLad.Lads)
+ for i := len - 2; i >= 0; i-- { //機率會從大到小 一開始進去是第二大的機率(len-2)
+ smallerProbData := addrLad.Lads[i]
+ biggerProbData := addrLad.Lads[i+1]
+ if reflect.DeepEqual(smallerProbData.JtoO, biggerProbData.JtoO) {
+ addrLad.Lads = append(addrLad.Lads[:i], addrLad.Lads[i+1:]...)
+ }
+ }
+ }
+
+ return
+}

+ IsDefault bool `gorm:"not null"`

+ Juices JuicesHash `gorm:"type:json"` //為了做 某水位是否存在 的查詢操作而設計為map
+}

+ Juice uint `gorm:"not null;unique_index:idx_uni"`

+func (hdr *handler) DeleteTemplate(input *DeleteTemplateInputDto) (output DeleteTemplateOutputDto, errcode errors.Code) {
+
+ //如果不存在 當作刪除成功
+ tp := hdr.FuncGetTemplate(input.TemplateID)
+ if tp.ID == 0 {
+ output = DeleteTemplateOutputDto{
+ TemplateID: input.TemplateID,
+ }
+ return
+ }
+
+ // 不可刪預設
+ if tp.IsDefault {
+ errcode = errors.CannotDeleteDefault
+ return
+ }
+
+ leagues := []entities.League{}
+ hdr.db.Where("template_id = ?", input.TemplateID).Find(&leagues)
+ if len(leagues) > 0 {
+
+ template := entities.Template{}
+ hdr.db.
+ Where(&entities.Template{
+ SportID: leagues[0].SportID,
+ IsDefault: true,
+ }).First(&template)
+
+ if template.ID == 0 {
+ errcode = errors.RecordNotFound //找不到預設樣板可以取代 所以無法刪除使用者樣板
+ return
+ }
+
+ for idx := range leagues {
+ leagues[idx].TemplateID = template.ID //有使用即將被刪除的樣板之聯盟們 都會改套在預設樣板
+ if err := hdr.db.Save(leagues[idx]).Error; err != nil {
+ errcode = errors.Database
+ return
+ }
+ }
+ }
+
+ //刪子樣板
+ tpSubIds := hdr.funcGetIDs("template_subs", "template_id", input.TemplateID)
+ tpSubs := hdr.funcGetTemplateSubs(tpSubIds)
+ if err := hdr.db.Delete(&tpSubs).Error; err != nil {
+ errcode = errors.Database
+ return
+ }
+
+ //刪母樣板
+ if err := hdr.db.Delete(&tp).Error; err != nil {
+ errcode = errors.Database
+ return
+ }
+
+ output = DeleteTemplateOutputDto{
+ TemplateID: input.TemplateID,
+ }
+
+ return
+}

+ errcode = errors.Parameter
+ return

+ templateSub.OddsMin = input.OddsMin

+func findOdds(lid uint, opid uint, juice uint, prob float64) (float64, error) {
+
+ inputKey := getKey(lid, opid, juice, prob)
+
+ odds, oddsPre, targetKey, targetKeyPre := searchCeilingOdds(inputKey)
+
+ if inputKey-inputKey%10000 != targetKey-targetKey%10000 {
+ if inputKey-inputKey%10000 != targetKeyPre-targetKeyPre%10000 {
+ return 0, errors.Errorf("prob not found, inputKey:%v targetKey:%v", inputKey, targetKey)
+ }
+ return oddsPre, nil
+ }
+ return odds, nil
+}
+
+func searchCeilingOdds(target uint64) (float64, float64, uint64, uint64) {
+
+ l := 0
+ r := len(ObjLadderSub.Lads) - 1
+
+ mid := (l + r) / 2
+
+ for l <= r {
+
+ if ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key == target {
+ if mid >= 1 {
+ return ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid-1].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid-1].key
+ }
+ return ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key
+ }
+ if ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key > target {
+ r = mid - 1
+ } else {
+ l = mid + 1
+ }
+ mid = (r + l) / 2
+ }
+
+ if mid != len(ObjLadderSub.Lads)-1 && target > ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key {
+ mid++
+ }
+ if mid >= 1 {
+ return ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid-1].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid-1].key
+ }
+ return ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].odds, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key, ObjLadderSub.Lads[mid].key
+}
+
+func getKey(lid uint, opid uint, juice uint, prob float64) uint64 {
+
+ lid *= 10000000000
+ opid *= 1000000000
+ juice *= 100000
+ prob *= 100
+
+ return uint64(lid + opid + juice + uint(prob))
+}

+// GCD 找最大公因數(整數)
+func GCD(a, b int) int {
+ if a == 0 {
+ return b
+ }
+ return GCD(b%a, a)
+}
+
+// MultiplierToMakeWholeNum 找出一個浮點數要乘上多少(10^n)才會變成整數 ex: 10 or 100 or 1000 ...
+func MultiplierToMakeWholeNum(v float64) int {
+ s := strconv.FormatFloat(v, 'f', -1, 64)
+ i := strings.IndexByte(s, '.')
+ if i > -1 {
+ place := len(s) - i - 1
+ return int(math.Pow(float64(10), float64(place)))
+ }
+ return 1
+}
+
+// FindGCD 找最大公因數(浮點數)
+func FindGCD(arr []float64) float64 {
+
+ oneZeros := -1
+ for _, val := range arr {
+ temp := MultiplierToMakeWholeNum(val)
+ if oneZeros < temp {
+ oneZeros = temp
+ }
+ }
+
+ arr2 := make([]int, len(arr))
+
+ for idx, val := range arr {
+ arr2[idx] = int(val * float64(oneZeros))
+ }
+
+ result := arr2[0]
+
+ for _, val := range arr2 {
+ result = GCD(val, result)
+ }
+
+ return float64(result) / float64(oneZeros)
+}
+
+//RoundToBase 修飾到最接近的base倍數
+func RoundToBase(input float64, base float64) float64 {
+
+ temp := 1 / base
+ input = RoundTo(input*temp, 0)
+ rtn := math.Round(input/base) * base / temp
+
+ return rtn

+ err := db.AutoMigrate(
+ &entities.Ladder{}, //加table
+ &entities.LadderSub{}, //加table
+ ).Error
+ if err != nil {
+ return err
+ }

+ //從檔案導到結構
+ sheets, err := entities.GetLadderSheetObj()

+func funcGetLadderSubUnscoped(db *gorm.DB, ladderID uint, prob float64, optionID int, juice uint) (e entities.LadderSub) {
+ db.Unscoped().
+ Where("ladder_id = ?", ladderID).
+ Where("prob = ?", prob).
+ Where("option_id = ?", optionID).
+ Where("juice = ?", juice).
+ First(&e)
+ return
+}
+
+func funcUnscopedGetLadder(db *gorm.DB, id uint) (e entities.Ladder) {
+ db.Unscoped().Where("id = ?", id).First(&e)
+ return
+}
+
+//CheckLadderSheet 檢查ladder sheet符合規範
+func CheckLadderSheet(sheets entities.LadderSheets) (err error) {
+
+ haveOneWay := false
+ haveTwoWay := false
+ haveThreeWay := false
+ for idx := range sheets.Sheets {
+ ldSht := sheets.Sheets[idx]
+
+ if ldSht.IsDefault && ldSht.OptionCount == 1 {
+ if !haveOneWay {
+ haveOneWay = true
+ continue
+ }
+ return errors.New("more than 1 default ladder")
+ }
+ if ldSht.IsDefault && ldSht.OptionCount == 2 {
+ if !haveTwoWay {
+ haveTwoWay = true
+ continue
+ }
+ return errors.New("more than 1 default ladder")
+ }
+ if ldSht.IsDefault && ldSht.OptionCount == 3 {
+ if !haveThreeWay {
+ haveThreeWay = true
+ continue
+ }
+ return errors.New("more than 1 default ladder")
+ }
+
+ }
+ if !haveOneWay || !haveTwoWay || !haveThreeWay {
+ return errors.New("no default ladder")
+ }
+
+ for idx := range sheets.Sheets {
+ ldSht := sheets.Sheets[idx]
+
+ if ldSht.LadderName == "" {
+ return errors.New("no ladder name")
+ }
+
+ if ldSht.OptionCount < 1 {
+ return errors.New("wrong option count")
+ }
+
+ if ldSht.Lads == nil || len(ldSht.Lads) < 2 { //給至少兩個梯度值 避免一些演算麻煩
+ return errors.New("wrong lads")
+ }
+
+ tempProb := -999999.9 //機率從小變大
+
+ for _, lad := range ldSht.Lads {
+
+ if _, ok := lad.JtoO[1000]; !ok {
+ return errors.New("no default juice")
+ }
+
+ if tempProb >= lad.Prob {
+ return errors.New("wrong prob")
+ }
+
+ if lad.Prob < 0 || lad.Prob > 100 {
+ return errors.New("wrong prob")
+ }
+ for _, oddses := range lad.JtoO {
+ if len(oddses) != ldSht.OptionCount {
+ return errors.New("wrong option count")
+ }
+ }
+
+ if lad.JtoO == nil || len(lad.JtoO) == 0 {
+ return errors.New("wrong juice odds")
+ }
+
+ tempProb = lad.Prob
+ }
+ }
+
+ return nil
+}
+
+//SaveLadder 從json檔移植梯度到資料庫
+func SaveLadder(sheets entities.LadderSheets, db *gorm.DB) (err error) {
+
+ e1 := entities.LadderSub{}
+ db.Delete(entities.LadderSub{})
+ db.First(&e1)
+ if e1.ID != 0 {
+ return errors.New("delete fail")
+ }
+
+ e2 := entities.Ladder{}
+ db.Delete(entities.Ladder{})
+ db.First(&e2)
+ if e2.ID != 0 {
+ return errors.New("delete fail")
+ }
+
+ for idx := range sheets.Sheets {
+ ldSht := sheets.Sheets[idx]
+
+ gcdInput := make([]float64, 0)
+
+ for idx := range ldSht.Lads {
+ ldsSht := ldSht.Lads[idx]
+
+ gcdInput = append(gcdInput, ldsSht.Prob)
+
+ for juice, oddses := range ldsSht.JtoO {
+
+ for optionIdx, odds := range oddses {
+ ldSub := funcGetLadderSubUnscoped(db, ldSht.LadderID, ldsSht.Prob, optionIdx+1, juice)
+
+ ldSub.OptionID = uint(optionIdx + 1)
+ ldSub.LadderID = ldSht.LadderID
+ ldSub.Model.DeletedAt = nil
+ ldSub.Prob = ldsSht.Prob
+ ldSub.Juice = juice
+ ldSub.Odds = odds
+
+ err = db.Unscoped().Save(&ldSub).Error
+ if err != nil {
+ return err
+ }
+ }
+ }
+ }
+
+ ld := funcUnscopedGetLadder(db, ldSht.LadderID)
+
+ ld.Model.ID = ldSht.LadderID
+ ld.Model.DeletedAt = nil
+ ld.Name = ldSht.LadderName
+ ld.OptionCount = ldSht.OptionCount
+ ld.Juices = entities.JuicesHash{}
+ ld.Probs = gcdInput
+ ld.IsDefault = ldSht.IsDefault
+ for idx2 := range sheets.Sheets {
+ if sheets.Sheets[idx2].LadderID == ldSht.LadderID {
+ var temp = make(map[uint]bool)
+ for juiceKey := range ldSht.Lads[0].JtoO {
+ temp[juiceKey] = true
+ }
+
+ ld.Juices = temp
+ break
+ }
+ }
+
+ err = db.Unscoped().Save(&ld).Error
+ if err != nil {
+ return err
+ }
+ }
+
+ return nil

+ return err
+ }

+ return errors.New("juice not exist")
+ }
+

+ TemplateID: tp.ID,

+ IsRunning: true,

+ TemplateInst: juice,

+ OddsMin: 0,
